{"word":"G4467 - ῥᾳδιούργημα - rhaidioúrgēma - hrad-ee-oorg'-ay-mah - Lewdness","slug":"G4467","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ῥᾳδιούργημα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>rhaidioúrgēma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hrad-ee-oorg'-ay-mah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Lewdness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C1;&#x0314;&#x03B1;&#x0345;&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03BF;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03B3;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B1; - rhadiourge&#x0304;ma</b> - <i>hrad-ee-oorg'-ay-mah</i><p/>From a compound of <b>&#x03C1;&#x0314;&#x03B1;&#x0345;&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>rhadios</b> (<i>easy</i>, that is, <i>reckless</i>) and <a href=\"#/G2041\">G2041</a>; <i>easy going behavior</i>, that is, (by extension) a <i>crime:</i> - lewdness."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4468\">G4468</a>"}]}